flowchart TB
    PLAN[Decide: plan with steps]
    PLAN --> STEP{Step type?}

    STEP -->|Safe| EXEC_SAFE[Execute: ticket or PR]
    EXEC_SAFE --> AUDIT1[Audit log]

    STEP -->|Restricted| OPA_CALL[Call OPA: allow?]
    OPA_CALL --> OPA_OK{OPA result}
    OPA_OK -->|Error / Timeout / Unavailable| DENY[Deny + escalation packet]
    OPA_OK -->|Deny| DENY
    OPA_OK -->|Allow| REQ[Create approval request]
    REQ --> WAIT[Wait for human]
    WAIT --> APPROVE{Approve?}
    APPROVE -->|Yes| EXEC_RESTRICTED[Execute e.g. GitOps PR]
    APPROVE -->|No| REJECT[Reject]
    EXEC_RESTRICTED --> AUDIT2[Audit log: who, when]
    REJECT --> AUDIT2
    DENY --> AUDIT2
